to send out a message.

00:05:15.370 --> 00:05:32.030 align:middle line:90%


00:05:32.030 --> 00:05:36.710 align:middle line:10%
>> I'm here, we all are
here to give a warning.

00:05:36.710 --> 00:05:41.030 align:middle line:84%
>> Animals die, the trees
dry up, people become ill.

00:05:41.030 --> 00:05:42.630 align:middle line:90%
