00:05:59.900 --> 00:06:00.700 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:06:00.700 --> 00:06:04.370 align:middle line:84%
Start to understand, or what
will happen, right, that's it.

00:06:04.370 --> 00:06:10.840 align:middle line:90%


00:06:10.840 --> 00:06:14.798 align:middle line:84%
Then they waited, watched,
and listened to nature.

00:06:14.798 --> 00:06:16.840 align:middle line:84%
>> A major earthquake hit
Japan Friday afternoon.

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:19.298 align:middle line:84%
